foliage_toggle_parent.componentleveltooltip: Hides the foliage of trees when zoomed close to them for improved visibility.

occlusion_toggle_parent.componentleveltooltip: Shows an occlusion outline around units when they are obscured by trees and buildings.

selection_outlines_toggle_parent.componentleveltooltip: Display outlines for units.Ticking the box turns them on for selected units, while always show turns them on without conditions.

target_parent.componentleveltooltip: Display fire arcs for missile units.

unit_aura_parent.componentleveltooltip: Display the inner radius of a character's leadership encourage aura.

unit_id_bars_parent.componentleveltooltip: Display unit health, leadership and ammunition bars above units.

unit_threat_parent.componentleveltooltip: Unit threat level shows relative strength of enemy units compared to selected unit.
